detail.name: Gotenks
detail.effect: [Activate Main] Place this card into its owner's Drop : If you have 10 or more cards in your Drop, play up to 1 <Son Goten> with a cost of 2 or less and up to 1 <Trunks : Youth> with a cost of 2 or less from your Drop in Rest Mode.
